data.description: Welcome Home! Beautiful fully renovated home - open and welcoming - Large living room with high ceilings - 3 spacious bedrooms upstairs - including a full bathroom in the primary suite - Wow factor lower level!! - 2 spacious bedrooms and full bathroom with an oversized open living area - lower level kitchenette makes the lower level ideal for an in law suite - sliding glass doors lead to a large fully fenced backyard with covered patio and firepit - Convenient location! 25 minutes to Fort Meade & NSA; 35 minutes to DC  **Seller offering to assist with rate buy-down or closing cost**
